   "content": "![图片](http://127.0.0.1:5030/image/25ce30df96f07c07ad2b674bc2496371,msg/attach/395e129f24f5bf00da88ea52e9acece5/2026-05/Img/3ba41e6b48d51c4fe07db4b210a42e27)",
